Ngeke sakufihla ukuthi abamhlophe bayawusebenzisa umhlaba. Futhi ngendlela egculisayo banazo zonke izinto zokuwusebenzisa. Thina sifuna umhlaba nje khona abangenawo ngisho ugandaganda lo. Uthi ufuna umhlaba kumnandi nje ukuthi nginendawo yami yona le engenziwa lutho, kwephucwe abantu abebesebenzisa umhlaba. Bengingafisa ukuthi sike sivule amehlo ke sicabange ngenye indlela. Angisho ukuthi amabhunu enza kahle athatha umhlaba wethu ngenkani kodwa ngithi ake sibuke ngenye indlela. Kungcono abamhlophe bakhokhe inyanga nenyanga kungenjalo sobulawa yindlala lapho engasekho lokhu kwangempela-ke amathuba emisebenzi. Buzokwakhe eMelmoth